                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Williams</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-05-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 13, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>In reply to my yesterday’s communication, asking for the application of the
                    treaty and protocol to the trial, two Americans, <hi rend="italic"
                        >Competitor</hi> crew, and suspension of execution in case of death sentence
                    until I could inform you, Captain-General advises me officially that American
                    citizens are tried according to the treaty between Spain and the United States,
                    and further that no death sentence will be executed without approval of His
                    Majesty’s Government.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
